🗝️ 📚
🧩 fibfib(n) 👉
   ❓ n ⚖️ 0 👉
      ✅ 0
   🔚
   ❓ n ⚖️ 1 👉
      ✅ 0
   🔚
   ❓ n ⚖️ 2 👉
      ✅ 1
   🔚
   ❗ 👉
      n1 ⬅️ 差(n, 1)
      n2 ⬅️ 差(n, 2)
      n3 ⬅️ 差(n, 3)
      fibfib1 ⬅️ fibfib(n1)
      fibfib2 ⬅️ fibfib(n2)
      fibfib3 ⬅️ fibfib(n3)
      ✅ 和(fibfib1, fibfib2, fibfib3)
   🔚
🔚
>>> fibfib(1) 
0
>>> fibfib(5) 
4
>>> fibfib(8) 
24
>>> fibfib(2) 
1
>>> fibfib(1) 
0
>>> fibfib(5) 
4
>>> fibfib(8) 
24
>>> fibfib(10) 
81
>>> fibfib(12) 
274
>>> fibfib(14) 
927